metadata.name: Golden Bone #1
metadata.description: A relic, gifted to the canines by Doge, on the day humankind ascended to the Moon. Our intellect and strength are a product of its vast powers. The JunkYard Labs have been working tirelessly to decipher esoteric inscriptions etched onto its surface. Some say it is a key to the mysteries of our past, present, and future.
